        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Preserving Existing Nuclear Energy Generation Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to establish (1) a program to evaluate nuclear reactors that are projected to cease operations due to economic factors and to allocate financial credits to certain reactors, and (2) a grant program to assist communities with revenue shortfalls due to closures of nuclear power plants.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
